title: NFL Week 14: Aaron Rodgers could mess up the NFC Playoff Picture
itunes:title: NFL Week 14: Aaron Rodgers could mess up the NFC Playoff Picture
description:
Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith look over the current NFL playoff picture, make some predictions on how it will look by the end of the season (based on predictive analytics), and preview all of the Week 14 games that could have big playoff implications.
